OL,3,CNotts County heading to Wembley for
OL,4,Cplay-off final
OL,6,FNotts County will be heading to
OL,7,FWembley for the League Two play-off
OL,8,Ffinal after winning in an East
OL,9,FMidlands derby.
OL,11,FNotts County went into the second leg
OL,12,Fof their semi-final match against
OL,13,FChesterfield with a one-goal lead.
OL,15,FThe Magpies held Chesterfield to a nil-
OL,16,Fnil draw at Meadow Lane, after winning
OL,17,Fone-nil in the first leg.
OL,19,FThey finished one place and one point
OL,20,Fabove Chesterfield in the Championship
OL,21,Ftable.
